Titolo: Remnant: From the Ashes

Anno: 2019

Descrizione: Remnant: From the Ashes is an action role-playing third-person shooter developed by Gunfire Games and published by Perfect World Entertainment. It was released for Microsoft Windows, PlayStation 4 and Xbox One on August 20, 2019 and for PlayStation 5 and Xbox Series X and Series S on May 13, 2021. The game received generally positive reviews upon release and more than 3 million copies have been sold.

